      "rationale": "Predicted NIH values compared against experimental means across 5 flow-speed combinations. Maximum deviation is 12.3% at the 2500 RPM / 7.5 LPM operating point. All 5 comparisons fall within the 15% acceptance band. Validation dataset covers exposure durations of 10 ms and above; sub-10 ms transient edge cases are not represented, a known limitation acknowledged in the validation result narrative."
