      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence closure selected based on literature consensus for rotating blood-contacting devices. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied. Sensitivity analysis comparing SST k-omega against realizable k-epsilon shows less than 8% difference in NIH. Model form is appropriate for the COU flow regime (Re 10,000–40,000 in impeller passages)."
    },
